{"tid":1546792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實黨鐵跳閘只係不滿黨鐵的最溫和嘅方法","createTime":"2019-09-06T12:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T12:42:50.000Z","uid":17472,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e4da886d94a884c32f953a8d3db6b2c90add54","tid":1546792,"uid":17472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:09:24.000Z","msg":"先唔講政治問題，而家只係講黨鐵呢幾年嘅表現，處理問題嘅手法，無論你係黃絲定藍絲，你願意每日奉獻自己辛苦得來嘅金錢去俾呢個問題多多，服務每況愈下嘅機構嗎？<br />\n<br />\n跳閘只係和平表達對黨鐵不滿嘅一種方法，我知道香港有好多人因為工作種種因素無法擺脫對黨鐵嘅依賴（包括我在內），但既然擺脫唔到，倒不如用跳閘呢種方法去表達自己嘅不滿。<br />\n<br />\n跳閘，由今天起。我今日跳咗啦，你呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740ac8de4235c9b829c41308435211b9eb4fe312","tid":1546792,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:09:39.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2729520b95a31531ef9ce3598b07674721a82968","tid":1546792,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:11:07.000Z","msg":"大型廣告牆"},{"pid":"f10e48508f3ea8345f4b9c12edeea5e8d877069f","tid":1546792,"uid":5422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:11:52.000Z","msg":"Metoo"},{"pid":"2d2ebdd75d7727dedf6c1aa83102bedee7d6bdf5","tid":1546792,"uid":17472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:17:41.000Z","msg":"全城跳閘，人人做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc20fe4d95eab45022002027fa5e6beebcfc83d1","tid":1546792,"uid":17472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc